===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

#{{intransitive}} To have or open into blossoms; to [[bloom]].
#{{intransitive}} To begin to thrive or flourish.

====Synonyms====
*(''have or open into blossoms''): [[bloom]], come into bloom, come into blossom, [[flower]]
